A: In addition to service manuals, there are a variety of other resources available to help you service your Seat Leon 1.9 TDI. These include online forums, YouTube videos, and auto parts stores. By taking advantage of these resources, you can learn from others' experiences, find step-by-step tutorials, and purchase the necessary parts and supplies.</p>